1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 6=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=Why Is It Not Him=

4
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:04,430
I want to see your face clearly.

5
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:14,070
Ying Du.

6
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:18,710
♪A weary bird sways the branches♪

7
00:01:20,220 --> 00:01:24,320
♪My heart feels a gentle bond♪

8
00:01:25,700 --> 00:01:28,060
♪Petals fall before the courtyard♪

9
00:01:28,390 --> 00:01:30,830
♪New sprouts cover the ground♪

10
00:01:31,510 --> 00:01:32,350
Ying Du!

11
00:01:34,430 --> 00:01:35,270
Ying Du!

12
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:40,100
♪You lean close, speaking softly♪

13
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:45,510
♪Your gaze blooms with grace♪

14
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:48,830
♪Affection fills the air♪

15
00:01:48,870 --> 00:01:49,710
Ying Du.

16
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,600
Che,

17
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:54,150
what brings you here?

18
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:55,960
I just wanted to see

19
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:56,970
if your injury is serious.

20
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,510
I'm really fine.

21
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:01,230
I'm really fine.

22
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,870
Che,

23
00:02:03,070 --> 00:02:03,960
I have urgent business.

24
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:04,850
I'll be leaving now.

25
00:02:04,860 --> 00:02:05,790
Zhaoli,

26
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,680
I've been back for days.

27
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,630
Why have you been avoiding me?

28
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:12,030
I...

29
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,800
As you know,

30
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,750
you're different to me.

31
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,680
We once made a promise

32
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:19,190
to get married when we grew up.

33
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:20,430
You were to be my bride.

34
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:22,710
Che,

35
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,190
that was just childhood talk.

36
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,570
You can't take that seriously.

37
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:30,150
Back then, we didn't understand

38
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:33,150
how it feels to love someone.

39
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:36,030
So,

40
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,520
I'm sorry, Che.

41
00:02:40,670 --> 00:02:42,920
I don't believe there's no place
for me in your heart.

42
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,560
Have your people never told you

43
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,280
I'm Zhaoli's husband?

44
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,030
If you keep pestering Zhaoli,

45
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:58,400
saying she's your bride,

46
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,360
this warning will be the least
of your worries.

47
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:07,710
(Ying Du's power has clearly waned.)

48
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,000
(How did his injuries heal so quickly?)

49
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,030
(Could it be)

50
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:14,120
(because he's been with Wu Zhaoli?)

51
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,520
Ying Du,

52
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,960
I can handle it myself.

53
00:03:31,610 --> 00:03:32,810
The old wounds haven't healed,

54
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:33,970
and now there are new ones.

55
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:35,150
You get hurt too easily;

56
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,660
I can't keep protecting you like this.

57
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:40,090
No wonder you agreed to my deal
without hesitation yesterday.

58
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:40,970
It seems

59
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,800
I've made a losing bargain.

60
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:48,710
Ying Du,

61
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,280
the man I saw in my dream

62
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,080
was you,

63
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,240
wasn't it?

64
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,200
What do you mean?

65
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:03,920
I said

66
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,870
the one I saw in my dream

67
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,750
was you.

68
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,000
See? It hasn't changed at all.

69
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:23,800
I'm not the one from your dream.

70
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,270
How could that be?

71
00:04:27,070 --> 00:04:28,800
I saw your face on him.

72
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,950
Now that you know I'm not him,

73
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,800
are you disappointed?

74
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,400
I...

75
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,800
I don't know.

76
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,560
It's all right.

77
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:47,600
Someday, you'll find out who he is.

78
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,830
I'll help you look for him.

79
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,600
The man Zhaoli's been seeing
is shameless.

80
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,680
He locked me up in the chicken coop!

81
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:07,240
These chickens kept me busy
for two days.

82
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,310
Help!

83
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,190
Help me!

84
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,920
Help!

85
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,800
Wu Luoluo?

86
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,950
I've been looking for you for two days.

87
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:18,720
I didn't expect to find you here.

88
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:21,120
Your Highness,

89
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:23,480
I followed your orders exactly.

90
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:26,070
But her lover got in the way.

91
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:29,310
You wouldn't blame me, right?

92
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:30,600
Since it's unfinished,

93
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,600
keep working for me.

94
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,680
If you fail this time,

95
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,360
you know the consequences.

96
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:45,190
I am Oracle,

97
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,350
(Oracle)
well-versed in the past and present.

98
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:50,000
There's nothing I don't know.

99
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:51,730
Zhaoli,

100
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,800
you're here again.

101
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:56,040
Are you here to interpret a dream

102
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:59,240
or to keep asking about the Bracelet?

103
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,080
Oracle,

104
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:03,750
could the person
confirmed by the Bracelet

105
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:05,630
be mistaken?

106
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,600
Is there any chance

107
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,800
that the Bracelet made an error?

108
00:06:10,950 --> 00:06:12,360
Absolutely impossible.

109
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,070
Sachets! Pouches!

110
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:21,040
Come and take a look!

111
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,010
Miss,

112
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:23,070
anything you fancy?

113
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:25,390
(The man in my dream isn't Ying Du.)

114
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:28,240
(Why does my heart feel so hollow?)

115
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,270
(She's so obsessed
with finding that man.)

116
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:31,960
(I should've said)

117
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,870
(that the man in her dream was me.)

118
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,200
(Otherwise,)

119
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,270
(if she finds that man,)

120
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,630
(would there be no place for me?)

121
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:40,400
Miss, have a look.

122
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:41,510
Miss, take a glance.

123
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:48,430
Sorry, are you alright?

124
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,600
My belly...

125
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,510
I think the baby is coming.

126
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,230
I beg you.

127
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,800
Please save my child and me.

128
00:06:58,070 --> 00:06:59,190
I may be a healer,

129
00:06:59,210 --> 00:07:00,530
but I've never delivered a baby.

130
00:07:00,530 --> 00:07:01,470
From the looks of this,

131
00:07:01,470 --> 00:07:02,740
if the child doesn't come soon,

132
00:07:02,740 --> 00:07:04,620
both the mother and the child
will be in peril.

133
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:05,800
Please, help her.

134
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,040
I'm begging you.

135
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:09,120
Please, save me.

136
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,360
Then come with me.

137
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,150
Watch your step.

138
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,420
Let's head over there.

139
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,510
May I borrow your umbrella?

140
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,360
Go find the nearest midwife.

141
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:22,040
I'll ease her pain first.

142
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,160
You must hurry.

143
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:24,150
Alright.

144
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:26,160
Careful.

145
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,000
Come on.

146
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,630
We'll make do here for now.

147
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,920
The midwife will be here soon.

148
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,390
You're not pregnant.

149
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,950
Wu Luoluo?

150
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,950
Was last time's lesson not enough?

151
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:09,920
You're working together.

152
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,310
From the looks of this,

153
00:08:14,310 --> 00:08:15,510
if the child doesn't come soon,

154
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,750
both mother and child will be in peril.

155
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:18,920
Then come with me.

156
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:24,350
Something's off.

157
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,440
Here you are, sir.

158
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,400
Got it.

159
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:39,810
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

160
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:46,610
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

161
00:08:48,070 --> 00:08:51,350
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

162
00:08:51,350 --> 00:08:54,250
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

163
00:08:54,770 --> 00:09:00,060
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

164
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:03,760
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

165
00:09:04,110 --> 00:09:06,460
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

166
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:10,500
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

167
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:12,880
♪And that is enough♪

168
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:16,670
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

169
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:19,640
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

170
00:09:20,010 --> 00:09:25,760
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

